 chapter of the Gita is a Yoga? Arjuna's depression is also named as Yoga -=
 Arjunavishad Yoga. [So many people get depressed about so many things dail=
y, yet what exactly is special about Arjuna's depression, or what is that d=
epression which when it afflicts someone makes him/her=C2=A0 fit for receiv=
ing Divine knowledge?]

Therefore, IMO, one does not really go into Gyana Y=
oga by bypassing or staying away from Karma Yoga. As Karma Yoga gets perfec=
ted, automatically a higher Gyana comes into the seeker. And so
 on..

